entries.s_dc95008b: We'll soon find out which one of you is the best. I want you to go after him.
entries.s_dfcc11ba: Yes, about that assault. It was effective - perhaps too effective.
entries.s_e19c193f: That Imperial Security Officer has provided us with a tremendous amount of information. With it, we can launch attacks that will decimate the Imperial fleet's infrastructure.
entries.s_e24417b: He will help us to plan an attack on Dathomir prison.
entries.s_e3d61563: Bomb-making material, Imperial comlinks, schematics - anything suspicious.
entries.s_e5235eff: Do you have a mission for me?
entries.s_e68c0bb8: Anyone who believes that is an idiot!
entries.s_eb3726f6: Yes. You're going to help me get information - from an Imperial defector.
entries.s_ec44bbf0: We are interested in an Imperial Security Officer. He has information we need.
entries.s_ecb17e60: I don't know what you mean
entries.s_ed4e5e50: Sure was. Do you have my next mission?
entries.s_f72b6d44: Would you like to learn a new skill now?
entries.s_f9044504: There's more I could teach you.
entries.s_f9e6ef1b: I do. There's a prisoner on Dathomir we wish to meet.
entries.s_f9f2fe5c: I like to know who I'm dealing with.
entries.s_fa38c858: I thought I was working for you.
entries.s_fa6e2383: Looks like our information was correct. Thank you for your efforts. Are you ready for a new skill?
entries.s_fab55d44: I know a smuggler. He works with Nym. And now he's going to work with you.
entries.s_fb871ded: Central Command has issued new orders for you.
entries.s_fd8741c0: I'm not scared of things that go bump in the night.
entries.s_ff8b2372: Correct. They are fiercely guarding something there. Do you know anything about it?
